                <p rend="flushleft">I <hi rend="italic">Report of the Deputies</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council approved the Deputies’ Report presented by the Chairman of the
                    day.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">II <hi rend="italic">Approval of the Minutes of Previous
                        Meetings</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council approved the minutes of its 27th, 28th and 29th meetings.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">III <hi rend="italic">Agenda</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council arranged its agenda for this meeting as follows: <list>
                        <label>1.</label>
                        <item>Peace Conference (draft invitations and rules of procedure)</item>
                        <pb facs="0840" n="816" xml:id="pg_816"/>
                        <label>2.</label>
                        <item>Italian reparation (final text)</item>
                        <label>3.</label>
                        <item>German questions</item>
                    </list>
                </p>
                <p rend="flushleft">IV <hi rend="italic">Peace Conference</hi> (Draft invitations
                    and rules of procedure)</p>
                <p>The Ministers had an exchange of views on this question.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">V <hi rend="italic">Italian Reparation</hi> (Final text)</p>
                <p>Deferred.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">VI <hi rend="italic">Next Meeting of the Council</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Monday, July 8, at 11:30 a.m.</p>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris, July</hi> 8, 1946.</p>
